I'm okay.

00:19:27.510 --> 00:19:28.670
Why are you here?

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:31.210
It's nothing.

00:19:31.210 --> 00:19:32.720
You called me

00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:33.790
but you didn't say anything.

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:34.510
I was worried about you,

00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:35.440
so I came over.

00:19:45.490 --> 00:19:46.890
What are you looking for?

