Is he dead or not?

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:36.310
That's impossible.

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.130
It's clearly...

00:20:45.590 --> 00:20:46.270
Ximei.

00:20:50.820 --> 00:20:52.890
It's not safe here anymore.

00:20:55.920 --> 00:20:57.320
We need to leave quickly.

