00:21:08.550 --> 00:21:09.810
The insurance company

00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:13.420
says it doesn't meet
the compensation conditions.

00:21:13.710 --> 00:21:14.710
What should we do?

00:21:16.030 --> 00:21:17.560
What should we do, Xiaojun?

00:21:19.990 --> 00:21:20.630
What if...

00:21:21.270 --> 00:21:22.800
What if the police find out?

00:21:42.240 --> 00:21:43.100
Let's run away.

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:46.130
Let's go somewhere else first.

00:21:46.350 --> 00:21:47.610
Our lives are at stake.

00:21:47.830 --> 00:21:49.030
We can run,

00:21:51.030 --> 00:21:52.960
but what about Tianbao's illness?

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:55.550
Jiaonan.

00:21:58.200 --> 00:21:59.330
Let's go to Jiaonan.

00:22:04.550 --> 00:22:05.240
In Jiaonan,

00:22:05.310 --> 00:22:07.970
there should be a way
to cure Tianbao's illness.

00:22:08.750 --> 00:22:09.950
I've told you before.

00:22:11.790 --> 00:22:13.990
Even if I have to sell my blood or organs,

00:22:15.880 --> 00:22:17.680
I'll save Tianbao's life.

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:20.420
Let's leave Weihai first.

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:23.350
Early tomorrow morning,

00:22:23.350 --> 00:22:24.810
I'll go find the boat boss.

00:22:29.720 --> 00:22:31.270
I'm so tired, Xiaojun.

00:22:33.580 --> 00:22:35.640
I don't want to keep running anymore.

00:22:42.270 --> 00:22:43.970
When will this end?

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:45.970
Don't be afraid, Ximei.

00:22:47.970 --> 00:22:49.200
No matter what happens,

00:22:49.200 --> 00:22:50.590
I'll always be with you.

00:22:53.240 --> 00:22:54.880
I'll stay by your side.

00:22:59.830 --> 00:23:01.640
How did we end up like this?

00:23:05.620 --> 00:23:06.500
How did we

00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:08.550
come to this?

