[Fortune]

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:18.750
Coming.

00:23:22.350 --> 00:23:22.960
Ximei.

00:23:23.510 --> 00:23:24.240
You don't need

00:23:24.240 --> 00:23:25.300
to bring anything.

00:23:25.310 --> 00:23:26.110
It's so hot today,

00:23:26.110 --> 00:23:27.160
and I have to trouble you.

00:23:27.160 --> 00:23:27.620
Ximei.

00:23:27.920 --> 00:23:28.680
Give it to me.

