I'll go make dinner.

00:24:02.790 --> 00:24:03.440
Okay.

00:24:03.920 --> 00:24:04.920
Which one do you like?

00:24:04.920 --> 00:24:05.820
I like this one.

00:24:07.790 --> 00:24:08.790
Do you remember

00:24:08.830 --> 00:24:10.270
the boss of that moving company

00:24:10.270 --> 00:24:11.800
when we first started moving business?

00:24:11.800 --> 00:24:13.010
Mr. Wang?

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:14.630
What? Are you still in touch?

00:24:14.630 --> 00:24:15.430
No.

00:24:15.830 --> 00:24:17.850
I just saw their moving truck today.

00:24:18.100 --> 00:24:19.490
Hu was still driving.

00:24:19.880 --> 00:24:22.030
I just chatted with him briefly.

00:24:22.590 --> 00:24:24.240
Hu told me that...

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:28.590
Mr. Wang's nephew died.

00:24:29.110 --> 00:24:30.030
Died?

00:24:32.310 --> 00:24:33.240
Yes.

00:24:33.310 --> 00:24:33.840
Tianbao,

00:24:33.920 --> 00:24:35.780
go play by yourself inside, okay?

00:24:36.200 --> 00:24:37.270
Tianbao.

00:24:38.320 --> 00:24:39.360
Give me a kiss.

00:24:47.160 --> 00:24:48.070
How did he die?

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:49.030
I still remember

00:24:49.030 --> 00:24:50.350
his nephew's nickname,

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:51.200
Lei.

00:24:51.270 --> 00:24:52.160
Lei.

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:53.350
He was quite tall

00:24:53.880 --> 00:24:54.880
with yellow hair.

00:24:54.880 --> 00:24:55.640
He drove a small car,

00:24:55.640 --> 00:24:56.920
revving the engine all day,

00:24:56.920 --> 00:24:57.920
always racing.

00:24:58.350 --> 00:24:59.960
Nearly knocked me down once.

00:25:00.400 --> 00:25:01.240
Yeah.

00:25:01.750 --> 00:25:02.550
He just

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:04.920
crashed while racing,

00:25:05.160 --> 00:25:07.550
hitting a truck carrying steel bars.

00:25:07.920 --> 00:25:09.400
From his chest to his back,

00:25:09.830 --> 00:25:12.230
he was completely
impaled by the steel bar.

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:14.480
A hole this big.

00:25:15.790 --> 00:25:17.160
Terrible.

00:25:19.350 --> 00:25:21.680
The morning of the day
he had the accident,

00:25:21.750 --> 00:25:22.890
Lei took his cousin

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:24.200
to that tattoo parlor,

00:25:24.880 --> 00:25:26.510
and it happened that evening.

00:25:26.510 --> 00:25:27.270
You know why?

00:25:27.960 --> 00:25:30.560
He got a tattoo of
something he shouldn't have.

00:25:33.350 --> 00:25:35.830
He tattooed Guangong.

00:25:42.640 --> 00:25:44.440
Guangong.

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:46.970
You know where

00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:48.070
his wound was?

00:25:51.000 --> 00:25:53.000
Right on Guangong's head.

00:25:54.400 --> 00:25:55.460
Isn't that creepy?

00:25:57.640 --> 00:25:59.630
It's just superstition, of course.

00:25:59.630 --> 00:26:00.690
Let's not talk about it anymore.

00:26:00.690 --> 00:26:02.000
Respect the dead.

00:26:02.590 --> 00:26:03.440
Cheers.

00:26:04.160 --> 00:26:05.030
Therefore,

00:26:05.240 --> 00:26:07.310
when we drive in the future,

00:26:07.400 --> 00:26:09.640
we must pay attention to safety.

00:26:16.930 --> 00:26:18.410
Speaking of Guangong,

00:26:20.350 --> 00:26:21.610
I remember something.

00:26:26.620 --> 00:26:27.820
Do you want to hear it?

00:26:28.240 --> 00:26:28.950
Tell me.

00:26:29.000 --> 00:26:30.000
It's also creepy.

00:26:34.110 --> 00:26:35.030
Many years ago,

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:37.960
one night

00:26:39.110 --> 00:26:40.070
in the forest,

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:43.920
there was a man

00:26:45.710 --> 00:26:46.370
and a woman.

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:52.400
What were they doing?

00:26:53.270 --> 00:26:54.270
That man and woman

00:26:54.270 --> 00:26:55.880
were digging a hole.

00:27:02.880 --> 00:27:03.740
Digging a hole?

00:27:04.400 --> 00:27:05.240
Do you know what

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:06.170
they were doing?

00:27:09.070 --> 00:27:09.920
What?

00:27:14.960 --> 00:27:15.960
Burying the body.

00:27:22.090 --> 00:27:22.970
You know,

00:27:24.920 --> 00:27:26.110
why I thought of Guangong

00:27:26.110 --> 00:27:27.510
when telling this story?

00:27:28.030 --> 00:27:29.760
The man who was burying the body

00:27:30.680 --> 00:27:31.920
had a tattoo

00:27:35.410 --> 00:27:37.860
of Guangong on his back.

00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:42.130
Back then,

00:27:42.160 --> 00:27:43.510
didn't those gangsters

00:27:43.720 --> 00:27:44.480
all

00:27:44.590 --> 00:27:47.070
copy those triad members and get tattoos?

00:27:47.510 --> 00:27:49.510
Either Guangong or dragons.

00:27:50.160 --> 00:27:52.110
Seven or eight out of ten

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:53.310
would get Guangong tattoos.

00:27:53.310 --> 00:27:54.510
No,

00:27:54.590 --> 00:27:56.070
his Guangong tattoo

00:27:57.110 --> 00:27:59.000
wasn't an ordinary one.

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:03.640
He had a tattoo of Guangong
with open eyes.

00:28:05.560 --> 00:28:05.960
Do you know

00:28:05.960 --> 00:28:08.020
what a Guangong with open eyes means?

00:28:10.310 --> 00:28:12.440
I don't know if you believe this or not,

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:14.260
but as the saying goes,

00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:15.760
once Guangong

00:28:17.880 --> 00:28:18.680
open his eyes,

00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:24.010
blood will be spilled.

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:28.960
I scared you!

00:28:33.400 --> 00:28:34.030
And then?

00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:35.640
Then...

00:28:41.590 --> 00:28:42.830
I don't know.

00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:50.240
Later that friend got drunk.

00:28:57.720 --> 00:28:58.550
He was drunk?

00:28:58.640 --> 00:28:59.200
Yes.

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:11.480
Why didn't that man call the police?

00:29:11.640 --> 00:29:12.700
He was making it up.

00:29:12.750 --> 00:29:14.110
I think he was too drunk.

00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:16.800
In the middle of the night

00:29:17.640 --> 00:29:18.590
and in the wilderness,

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:19.920
you can't see anything.

00:29:20.440 --> 00:29:21.960
How could he see any Guangong tattoo?

00:29:21.960 --> 00:29:23.480
Finish this drink,

00:29:23.500 --> 00:29:24.700
then go back and rest.

00:29:24.720 --> 00:29:25.440
We have important things to do tomorrow.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:25.790
Yes.

00:29:25.820 --> 00:29:27.150
Do you know that person?

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:29.000
No.

00:29:29.880 --> 00:29:31.010
How would I know him?

00:29:31.440 --> 00:29:32.110
We were having dinner,

00:29:32.110 --> 00:29:33.400
and a friend brought him along.

00:29:33.400 --> 00:29:34.720
I heard him talking there.

00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:36.400
He was drunk and rambling.

00:29:45.920 --> 00:29:46.650
Take it easy.

00:29:48.550 --> 00:29:49.880
I'm drunk.

00:29:51.510 --> 00:29:52.500
Careful.

00:29:53.070 --> 00:29:53.630
Come.

00:29:54.270 --> 00:29:54.820
Okay!

00:29:54.880 --> 00:29:55.720
Be careful on your way.

00:29:55.720 --> 00:29:56.850
I can walk by myself.

00:29:57.790 --> 00:29:59.440
Don't you need me to see you off?

00:29:59.440 --> 00:30:00.920
No need.

00:30:03.750 --> 00:30:04.720
Get some rest.

00:30:04.750 --> 00:30:06.590
I'm leaving. Time to sleep.

