Did you actually see

00:34:26.070 --> 00:34:27.469
Dong's ID card back then?

00:34:29.400 --> 00:34:31.130
It was too chaotic at that time.

00:34:34.020 --> 00:34:34.840
No.

00:34:35.510 --> 00:34:36.440
I didn't notice.

00:34:36.670 --> 00:34:37.480
When I was cleaning up,

00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:38.739
I didn't see it either.

00:34:49.190 --> 00:34:49.920
Do you think...

