But if he saw it,

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:36.700
how could he...

00:35:37.110 --> 00:35:39.360
How could he act like nothing happened?

00:35:43.440 --> 00:35:44.670
And that scar of his,

00:35:48.060 --> 00:35:48.480
why

00:35:48.510 --> 00:35:50.170
is it in exactly the same place

00:35:50.190 --> 00:35:51.520
as Ni Xiangdong's scar?

