must be born in the Year of the Monkey,
just like him.

00:36:59.030 --> 00:36:59.250
Right.

00:36:59.250 --> 00:36:59.780
Tianbao,

00:36:59.840 --> 00:37:00.850
ask your Uncle Ni

00:37:00.880 --> 00:37:02.000
what his zodiac sign is.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:02.530
Uncle Ni,

00:37:02.550 --> 00:37:04.030
what's your zodiac sign?

00:37:06.550 --> 00:37:07.670
Mine is...

00:37:09.480 --> 00:37:10.080
the Horse.

00:37:12.760 --> 00:37:14.360
If you were born
in the Year of the Monkey like me,

00:37:14.360 --> 00:37:15.000
that would be great.

00:37:15.000 --> 00:37:16.600
We'd be just like Sun Wukong.

00:37:16.840 --> 00:37:17.580
Right.

00:37:17.630 --> 00:37:19.760
Sun Wukong can do 72 transformations.

00:37:20.230 --> 00:37:20.760
Uncle Ni,

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:22.280
if you could do 72 transformations,

00:37:22.280 --> 00:37:24.010
what would you transform into?

00:37:24.590 --> 00:37:26.450
If I could do 72 transformations,

00:37:26.510 --> 00:37:28.630
I'd definitely transform into Sun Wukong.

00:37:28.630 --> 00:37:29.610
Wouldn't there be two

00:37:29.610 --> 00:37:30.610
Sun Wukongs then?

00:37:30.670 --> 00:37:31.360
No,

00:37:31.710 --> 00:37:33.310
there's only one Sun Wukong.

00:37:33.670 --> 00:37:34.960
The other one would be

00:37:35.360 --> 00:37:36.760
the Six-Eared Macaque.

00:37:37.630 --> 00:37:39.670
He doesn't understand
what you're talking about.

00:37:39.670 --> 00:37:40.030
Come on.

00:37:40.030 --> 00:37:40.490
Come on.

00:37:40.920 --> 00:37:41.280
Blow out the candles.

00:37:41.280 --> 00:37:41.940
Make a wish.

00:37:43.400 --> 00:37:43.880
Come on.

00:37:44.400 --> 00:37:48.280
Happy birthday to you.

00:37:48.670 --> 00:37:52.400
Happy birthday to you.

00:37:52.710 --> 00:37:57.150
Happy birthday to you.

00:37:57.360 --> 00:38:01.880
Happy birthday to you.

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:04.960
Great!

00:38:05.510 --> 00:38:06.910
Let mommy give you a kiss.

00:38:07.030 --> 00:38:08.230
Happy birthday.

00:38:08.760 --> 00:38:10.150
Turn on the light.

00:38:11.230 --> 00:38:12.000
Tianbao.

00:38:12.070 --> 00:38:12.760
I want to have some cake.

00:38:12.760 --> 00:38:13.480
Study hard,

00:38:13.710 --> 00:38:14.880
and make progress every day.

00:38:14.880 --> 00:38:16.880
Cutting a big piece.

00:38:17.230 --> 00:38:18.190
Smaller.

00:38:18.630 --> 00:38:20.890
Have you forgotten what the doctor said?

00:38:23.590 --> 00:38:24.450
Is this enough?

00:38:26.760 --> 00:38:27.230
Here.

00:38:29.590 --> 00:38:30.630
Here.

00:38:31.000 --> 00:38:31.440
Ximei,

00:38:31.510 --> 00:38:32.840
I'm not drinking anymore.

00:38:32.840 --> 00:38:34.240
I got drunk the other day.

00:38:35.190 --> 00:38:36.840
What are you afraid of? We're family.

00:38:36.840 --> 00:38:37.700
Just one drink.

00:38:38.070 --> 00:38:38.400
Okay.

00:38:38.480 --> 00:38:38.960
One drink.

00:38:38.960 --> 00:38:39.690
Cao Tianbao.

00:38:40.800 --> 00:38:41.510
Didn't we agree

00:38:41.510 --> 00:38:42.800
to celebrate your birthday at my house?

00:38:42.800 --> 00:38:43.590
Alright, thank you.

00:38:43.590 --> 00:38:45.030
I'll show you my new doll.

00:38:45.590 --> 00:38:46.710
I haven't eaten yet.

00:38:46.710 --> 00:38:47.280
You eat first.

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:48.940
My grandma steamed some bass.

00:38:49.030 --> 00:38:49.760
It's okay, Tianbao,

00:38:49.760 --> 00:38:50.800
go have some bass.

00:38:51.760 --> 00:38:52.880
Lele, have a piece of cake.

00:38:52.880 --> 00:38:53.670
Yes.

00:38:54.030 --> 00:38:55.400
Take a piece of cake with you.

00:38:55.400 --> 00:38:57.530
-Thank you.
-Here's for your grandma.

00:38:57.670 --> 00:38:58.110
Right.

00:38:59.150 --> 00:39:00.760
Tianbao, help Lele take it.

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:01.320
Okay.

00:39:01.400 --> 00:39:02.690
-Stand there.
-Here, take the cake.

00:39:02.690 --> 00:39:03.520
Good boy.

00:39:03.760 --> 00:39:05.230
I will pick you up later.

00:39:07.550 --> 00:39:08.800
Tianbao always wants to play with Lele

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:10.280
after school every day.

00:39:10.510 --> 00:39:11.890
Well, he and Lele

00:39:12.070 --> 00:39:13.510
make a good match.

00:39:13.920 --> 00:39:14.800
Yes.

00:39:15.710 --> 00:39:16.550
Ni,

00:39:16.630 --> 00:39:18.560
in which year did you leave Jialin?

00:39:21.000 --> 00:39:21.880
I left

00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:23.840
in 2004.

00:39:24.670 --> 00:39:25.670
What a coincidence.

00:39:25.670 --> 00:39:26.280
What about you?

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:27.880
We also left in 2004.

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:28.400
Yes.

00:39:28.480 --> 00:39:30.210
Yes, the year Tianbao was born.

00:39:30.630 --> 00:39:31.590
What a coincidence.

00:39:31.590 --> 00:39:32.630
Yeah.

00:39:33.800 --> 00:39:34.460
Xiangdong,

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:36.320
I remember you mentioned

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:37.030
that

00:39:37.110 --> 00:39:37.920
the scar on your face

00:39:37.920 --> 00:39:39.710
was from a burn when you were a kid.

00:39:39.710 --> 00:39:40.840
But I noticed there's no scar

00:39:40.840 --> 00:39:42.040
on your ID card photo.

00:39:58.120 --> 00:39:59.620
When did you

00:40:00.350 --> 00:40:01.760
ever see my ID card?

00:40:03.590 --> 00:40:04.800
Why so nervous?

00:40:04.880 --> 00:40:05.710
I'm not.

00:40:06.360 --> 00:40:06.890
That day

00:40:06.920 --> 00:40:08.280
when we were getting
our driver's licenses,

00:40:08.280 --> 00:40:09.110
you went to the toilet

00:40:09.110 --> 00:40:10.920
and I took your ID card for you.

00:40:19.030 --> 00:40:19.960
Is it hard to say?

00:40:21.960 --> 00:40:22.630
No.

00:40:24.440 --> 00:40:25.280
Look at you.

00:40:25.850 --> 00:40:27.400
I'm just curious.

00:40:32.920 --> 00:40:33.760
Xiaojun,

00:40:34.550 --> 00:40:35.230
Ximei,

00:40:38.440 --> 00:40:39.360
actually, there's something

00:40:39.360 --> 00:40:40.440
I haven't told you.

00:40:44.000 --> 00:40:45.360
That ID card you saw

00:40:46.960 --> 00:40:48.160
isn't actually mine.

00:40:54.030 --> 00:40:54.960
Whose is it then?

00:40:55.630 --> 00:40:56.440
I don't know.

00:40:57.400 --> 00:40:58.150
I bought it.

00:40:59.920 --> 00:41:00.800
Bought it?

00:41:03.550 --> 00:41:04.710
Back then,

00:41:05.230 --> 00:41:06.560
I got into some trouble,

00:41:07.550 --> 00:41:08.610
and I found someone

00:41:09.590 --> 00:41:10.240
who had

00:41:10.280 --> 00:41:11.760
many fake ID cards.

00:41:13.000 --> 00:41:14.070
I spent 50 yuan

00:41:14.150 --> 00:41:14.920
to buy one.

00:41:27.670 --> 00:41:29.200
Now that I've told you this.

00:41:30.670 --> 00:41:31.400
I have nothing

00:41:31.400 --> 00:41:32.800
to hide from you anymore.

00:41:33.360 --> 00:41:34.760
You've been so good to me.

00:41:38.360 --> 00:41:40.070
So I'll tell you everything.

00:41:42.670 --> 00:41:44.330
My surname isn't actually Ni.

00:41:49.280 --> 00:41:50.010
My surname is

00:41:50.920 --> 00:41:51.510
Yu,

00:41:52.280 --> 00:41:53.810
and I'm from Yafen Village.

00:41:54.630 --> 00:41:55.760
At the end of 2003,

00:41:56.480 --> 00:41:58.880
I got into a conflict
with someone back home

00:41:59.400 --> 00:42:01.150
and accidentally stabbed him.

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:04.800
After that, I just kept running,

00:42:05.400 --> 00:42:06.800
hiding everywhere,

00:42:07.670 --> 00:42:08.710
wandering around,

00:42:08.710 --> 00:42:10.370
until I finally ended up here.

00:42:10.760 --> 00:42:12.120
I originally had

00:42:12.150 --> 00:42:13.280
no hope for my life.

00:42:14.000 --> 00:42:14.440
I just thought

00:42:14.440 --> 00:42:16.400
someday the police would arrest me.

00:42:16.400 --> 00:42:17.400
I'd get sentenced

00:42:17.480 --> 00:42:18.440
and go to prison.

00:42:19.190 --> 00:42:20.120
I wasn't afraid.

00:42:21.920 --> 00:42:23.480
But then I met you...

00:42:28.230 --> 00:42:29.480
And you gave me

00:42:30.670 --> 00:42:32.130
a feeling like home again.

00:42:33.760 --> 00:42:34.960
That's when I decided

00:42:35.230 --> 00:42:36.230
to stay here

00:42:37.070 --> 00:42:38.030
and settle down.

00:42:44.000 --> 00:42:45.030
Ni.

00:42:46.510 --> 00:42:47.240
Look,

00:42:47.280 --> 00:42:49.070
we don't mean anything else.

00:42:49.150 --> 00:42:49.760
Right.

00:42:50.110 --> 00:42:50.550
Yes.

00:42:53.480 --> 00:42:54.800
I just want to tell you.

00:42:55.070 --> 00:42:57.270
I don't want to hide it from you anymore.

00:42:57.280 --> 00:42:58.290
I really wasn't

00:42:58.360 --> 00:42:59.480
keeping it from you on purpose.

00:42:59.480 --> 00:43:00.810
How am I supposed to tell

00:43:00.960 --> 00:43:02.560
this kind of thing to anyone?

00:43:03.550 --> 00:43:04.480
Anyway, now

00:43:04.550 --> 00:43:06.010
I've told you everything.

00:43:06.550 --> 00:43:07.440
It's your own

00:43:07.550 --> 00:43:08.590
choice to make.